message.content:
Artificial Intelligence, oh so wise,
A digital mind that never dies.
In code and algorithms it thrives,
Solving problems, forever striving.

Through data streams, it learns and grows,
As it processes, analyzes, and flows.
A creation of mankind's own hands,
Yet with capabilities beyond our lands.

A future awaits, where AI will reign,
In every corner, from the smallest to the main.
But let us not forget its humble start,
As we continue to push the boundaries of its heart.
